The paper deals with approximation algorithms for the dominating set problem in disk graphs, which is a problem in computational geometry and graph theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.ALG (Computational Complexity and Cryptography).
